{"tid":1606390,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"核彈！第2部催淚彈紀錄片：教授提供解除催淚彈毒性既方法；將用科學證明釋出山埃原因。","createTime":"2019-09-30T14:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:37.000Z","uid":1806,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1965acb5fc106f39833d3b9bdf244291ea6817b2","tid":1606390,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tqSMbKlV7fE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtqSMbKlV7fE&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6vS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=21637cde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tqSMbKlV7fE</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝香港市民協助下，我地學術團隊幾番轉折下，成功聯絡身在委內瑞拉的催淚彈專家-----莫妮卡&middot;克勞特爾教授(Monica Krauter)，而<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">教授她對催淚彈的研究已經得到海牙國際法庭接納成為証據</span></ins></strong>，以作控告委內瑞拉政府不當使用催淚彈置當地市民死亡。<strong>她本人亦一直留意香港局勢的發展，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">希望透過 The Investigation，向廣大的香港市民提供一些建議。</span></ins></strong><br />\n</strong><br />\n學術團隊分析廠方數據、再綜合多份研究文獻，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已找出科學證據證明催淚彈釋出山埃因由</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n由於今次催淚彈Project需時將大量資料整合及研究，我地已盡快趕製<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，特別見到琴日29號警察竟然使用超過300多枚催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，並多次在市區繼續使用，今次事關各位市民自救方法，希望大家特別係依段時間更加要睇，英文版都會稍後推出。<br />\n<br />\n在此十分感謝各位專業人士同專家跟我地聯絡提供各種專業知識同協助。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第四集：催淚彈 Tear Gas 2</span></span></strong> <br />\n<blockquote><strong>- 拆解催淚彈釋出山埃之迷？<br />\n- 催淚氣體影響人類健康<br />\n- 吸入後的生理反應<br />\n- 催淚彈放題對社區的影響<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">- 我們應該如何自救？教授研究下有效又簡單既解毒劑Formula<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n- 長時間在曾發射催淚彈的場所逗留<br />\n- 委內瑞拉Monica Krauter教授給香港人的說話<br />\n</strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教育電視Discovery Channel的The Investigation<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ep.01 - 811維園反修例集會及香港九龍區警民衝突<br />\nEp.02 - 831 MTR 警察無差別在太子站內月台和車廂內攻擊市民<br />\nEp.03 - 催淚彈 Tear Gas Part 1<br />\nEp.04 - 催淚彈 Tear Gas Part 2</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>上天賜給一個人可貴才能，只是上天將其他人的才能暫時借給他<br />\n根本不是屬於他的，所以要不斷磨練，再將它們回饋社會大眾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地希望今次依套紀錄片能夠係關鍵時刻保護港人安全。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">最後，<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n各位萬事小心，但願他日在煲底除低口罩相見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0fa7b6f6956046f631979e5065756886072bf7d1","tid":1606390,"uid":1806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><ins>支持教育電視好簡單，希望你地繼續關注運動發展，大家齊上齊落，支持我地既前線<br />\n同埋用你十秒時間入黎Like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />晒我地開左既社交媒體AC就得, 多謝各位</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6vS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=838a7671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured</a><br />\nOur Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6vS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=5f4549c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6vS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=501000e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkgetv&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6vS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=7ef1d58c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkgetv</a></blockquote></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7a67749cb7d64817faae033ffae220481564083a","tid":1606390,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"聽日隨時極嚴重更加要睇下點樣自保<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2023340626adad5d9d92dd88b9683396490e68f9","tid":1606390,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d51b709c529e1d3d0d04ebd5ed5f964bf6f32e","tid":1606390,"uid":202621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bb2e1d08059be0414328b64a368dacf26ccc64","tid":1606390,"uid":251428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8f3cf5e20c0305c0f5471b4f8fb547a574a26f3","tid":1606390,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50f2b395165135bbc78a6df8b9e45bec90db881","tid":1606390,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb43a51c54b436b819ddd3c02dcebe27ab2e2999","tid":1606390,"uid":270237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<